text: sorry for the delay Frooque, it appears the html is the same. The only time it is not the same is if the form is set to use a theme. <https://designers.HubSpot.com/docs/cos/HubSpot-form-markup#form-themes-and-iframes>

if you look at the little help tooltip for that field in the inspector you will see it includes a `{{html}}` tag, this is the tag you wrap your code around, the module code will be injected into that.
